videos.headline: Burrow goes deep for 40-yard TD
videos.description: Joe Burrow finds an open Justin Jefferson for the easy 40-yard LSU touchdown.

videos.headline: Ball hits Arkansas receiver in face
videos.description: Arkansas tries to go deep but Cheyenne O'Grady can't get his hands up and the ball hits him square in the face.

videos.headline: LSU RB finds a hole and scores
videos.description: LSU running back Clyde-Edwards Helaire hits the hole and sprints his way to a 13-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Arkansas's O'Grady goes up and grabs the TD
videos.description: After getting hit in the face earlier in the game, Arkansas's Cheyenne O'Grady leaps high in the air for the 11-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Arkansas' O'Grady scores his second TD of the game
videos.description: Arkansas' Cheyenne O'Grady shows off the strength and powers his way into the end zone after hauling in the catch for a 32-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: LSU DB makes incredible one-handed INT
videos.description: LSU's Kary Vincent Jr. reaches back and makes the spectacular one-handed interception.
